text: The Chilean cricket team is the national cricket team of Chile. The team played its first international match in 1893, against Argentina. ==Tournaments== ===ICC Americas Championship=== * 2006: 3rd place (3rd division) * 2008: 2nd place. * 2009: 3rd place. == Other websites == * Official Website Category:1893 establishments Category:1890s establishments in South America Category:19th-century establishments in Chile Category:National sports teams of Chile
